==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wood partridge
<hw>Wood partridge</hw>. <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Any of several small
partridges of Java, Sumatra, Borneo, and neighboring regions belonging
to the genera <gen>Caloperdix</gen>, <gen>Rollulus</gen>, and
<gen>Melanoperdix</gen>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The Canada
grouse.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Woodpeck</ent>⟦br⟧
